&lt;h2&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-1324008" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250829_121252_-1280x720.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="720" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250829_121252_-scaled.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250829_121252_-694x390.jpg 694w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;G6 亦是暫時全港唯一具備遙控泊車功能 SUV，標配自動泊車與離車遙控泊車功能，即使無停車位亦可自動泊入。另支援一鍵倒車，配合透明底盤與窄路影像輔助，解決香港狹窄道路調頭難題。G6 搭載 12 個超聲波 + 5 個毫米波雷達與 12 個高清鏡頭組合而成的 Lofic 鷹眼視覺方案，識別物件速度提高了 40%，感知距離亦增加了 125%，結合高效能的 NVIDIA Orin 晶片，高解像度探測周圍環境，於低能見度和強光等條件下依然精準駕駛。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-1324011" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250829_115100-1280x720.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="720" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250829_115100-scaled.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250829_115100-694x390.jpg 694w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-1324005" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250829_121451-1280x720.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="720" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250829_121451-scaled.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250829_121451-694x390.jpg 694w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;售價方面，2025 款 G6 後驅版定價 279,900 港元起，四驅版 299,900 港元起，早鳥優惠後驅版 269,900 港元，四驅版 289,900 港元，優惠需符合一換一要求並經香港海關最終批核。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-large wp-image-1324012" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250829_114901-1280x720.jpg" alt="" width="1280" height="720" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250829_114901-scaled.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/img_20250829_114901-694x390.jpg 694w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
